      "role": "user",
      "content": "treatments dont do anything anymore. i've tried everything. it's not about 'coping' or finding 'strategies', it's just... some things aren't meant to be fixed. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually get some peace and quiet from the noise in my nerves is to just not be here. like, isn't there a certain kind of mercy in just letting go when the suffering is this much?",
